<div class="allianceSection collapsable collapsed">
	 <h4 class="header">Fire Characteristics</h4>
	<div class="text">Fire fuels and ignition rates are naturally low. Other disturbances, such as shifting rock/soil, blow-outs, and burial and erosion along cliffs and steep slopes, are typical forces of change in this alliance.</div>
